    "intro": "Welcome to Phoenix Blossom Crossroads — a second-hand vinyl record trading platform for music lovers.",
    "whatWeDo": {
      "title": "What We Do",
      "text": "We believe every vinyl record has its own unique story. Our platform connects record enthusiasts and collectors, helping great music find new homes. Whether it's classic rock, jazz, classical, or pop, you'll find your next favorite record here."
    },
    "whyVinyl": {
      "title": "Why Vinyl",
      "text": "Vinyl records are more than just a music format — they're a culture. The warm sound quality, beautiful cover art, and collectible value are things digital music cannot replace. We hope to help more people experience the magic of vinyl through this platform."
